  Koh, lang5 chit8-si-li5-a2 e5 liam7-thau5 ia7 tioh8 ti5-hong5. Na7 u7 bo5 chheng-khi3 e5 liam7- thau5 seN-khi2, chhin-chhiuN7 pang3 hoe2-chheng3 chit8-iuN7, pang3 hoe2-chheng3 tioh8 saN-hang7 chiau5-pi7; 1, chheng3; 2, hoe2-ioh8; 3, hoe2; khiam3 chit8 hang7 chiu7 be7-eng7-tit; hoe2 chit8-e7 chhuh tioh8 hoe2-ioh8, chheng3 chiu7 tan5, chiong hoe2 chhe3 hoa, chheng3 chiu7 be7 hiang2. Lang5 teh cho3 su7, u7 sin-khu, u7 sim, u7 liam7-thau5; sim seN-khi2 liam7-thau5, liam7-thau5 chit8-e7 hoat, sin-khu than3 i-e5 ho7-heng7, liam7-thau5 bo5 seN-khi2, sin-khu tek-khak be7 khi3 kiaN5, na7 e7 ap-che3 bo5 chheng-khi3 e5 liam7-thau5, sin-khu tek-khak bo5 cho3 put-hoat e5 su7-toan, chhin-chhiuN7 chhe3-hoa hoe2, chheng3 bo5 lou7-eng7, chiu7 be7 hai7 lang5 lah. Lang5 tioh8 sam3-su iau2 u7 kek8 phaiN2 e5 hoat-tou7, chiu7- si7 choan oe7 chhun-kiong-tou5, kek8 chin7 ki- khiau2 e5 kang-hu, ng3-bang7 than3 toa7 chiN5, bo5 siuN7 lang5 khoaN3 tioh8 che tou5 e7 pai7-hoai7 sim-sut8, chhoa7 lang5 im5-iok8 bo5 pat8-hang7 pi2 che khah siong-tiong7; in-ui7 lang5 khoaN3 tioh8 chit-ho7 tou5, put-lun7 kiaN5 che7 long2 teh siuN7 bo5 an-hun7 siu2-ki2 e5 su7, ti3-kau3 lam5-jin5 sit tek, hu7-li2 pai7 chiat, piN3 cho3 khim5-siu3, put seng5 jin5-lui7; che long2 tui3 oe7-tou5 hou7 lang5 an2-ni, kiam2 m7 si7 kek8 phaiN2? 
